HEADWORD: Commentation
<hw>Com`men*ta"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The act or process of commenting or criticising; exposition.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
